function VotingInfo({ info }) { return (
Missed Vote Percentage {info.missed_votes_pct}%
Votes with Party Percentage {info.votes_with_party_pct}%
Votes against Party Percentage {info.votes_against_party_pct}
Total Present Votes {info.total_present}
Total Votes {info.total_votes}
); } export default VotingInfo;
